      <title>欧盟将 28 名白俄罗斯个人列入制裁名单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/eu-adds-28-individuals-from-belarus-to-sanctions-list</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟将 28 名白俄罗斯个人列入制裁名单，其中包括高级公务员、法官和国家媒体高层人士，以惩罚他们持续镇压内部异议和侵犯人权的行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/eu-adds-28-individuals-from-belarus-to-sanctions-list</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:56:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者质疑尼日利亚在抗议活动中改革的决心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/investors-question-nigeria-s-resolve-on-reforms-amid-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者质疑政府的经济改革计划是否会因大规模抗议活动而脱轨，尼日利亚美元债券周一有望创下 17 个月以来的最大跌幅之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/investors-question-nigeria-s-resolve-on-reforms-amid-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:21:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国极右翼暴乱：南港谋杀案后为何爆发暴力事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/uk-far-right-riots-why-violence-erupted-after-southport-murders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国遭遇了十多年来最严重的骚乱，最初是由英格兰西北部三名女孩被谋杀而引发的，随后演变为全国极右翼团体的反移民和种族主义暴力。英国首相凯尔·斯塔默表示，暴徒将面临“法律的全面制裁”，但这场骚乱凸显出，工党在选举中取得压倒性胜利掩盖了极端政治边缘势力试图利用的深刻分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/uk-far-right-riots-why-violence-erupted-after-southport-murders</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:20:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本股市崩盘后日本央行加息时机遭批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/boj-under-fire-for-rate-hike-timing-after-japan-market-meltdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行上周收紧货币政策引发了一波批评，因为这导致日本股市历史性暴跌，并加剧了全球市场动荡 —— 有可能使任何进一步加息的计划被搁置。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/boj-under-fire-for-rate-hike-timing-after-japan-market-meltdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 13:37:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默承诺将派遣“大批”警察来应对任何进一步的骚乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/uk-blasts-hostile-states-musk-over-online-posts-as-riots-rage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默政府表示，外国可能参与煽动过去一周席卷英国的骚乱浪潮，首相承诺将“全力”打击肇事者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/uk-blasts-hostile-states-musk-over-online-posts-as-riots-rage</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 13:19:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>红州共和党人表示将捍卫拜登时代的绿色就业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/red-state-republicans-say-they-ll-defend-biden-era-green-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在那些从《通胀削减法案》中获得清洁能源投资的地方，共和党政客表示，他们会对可能危及清洁能源投资的变化发出警告。 ]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/red-state-republicans-say-they-ll-defend-biden-era-green-jobs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 13:00:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东局势紧张 普京安全委员会主席访问伊朗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/putin-s-security-council-chief-visits-iran-amid-mideast-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在伊朗伊斯兰共和国可能因哈马斯领导人之死对以色列发动报复性袭击的紧张局势加剧之际，俄罗斯安全委员会秘书谢尔盖·绍伊古访问了伊朗，与伊朗总统马苏德·佩泽什基安和高级官员举行会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/putin-s-security-council-chief-visits-iran-amid-mideast-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 11:55:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国总理哈西娜逃亡至伦敦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/bangladesh-s-hasina-headed-to-london-after-fleeing-country</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，谢赫·哈西娜在数千名抗议者的压力下于周一辞去孟加拉国总理一职，预计将前往伦敦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/bangladesh-s-hasina-headed-to-london-after-fleeing-country</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 11:51:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>总理逃亡后，孟加拉国军队将组建政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/bangladesh-leader-has-left-country-amid-protests-newspaper-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国总理谢赫·哈西娜在数百万抗议者的压力下于周一辞职逃离该国，该国陆军参谋长表示将努力组建临时政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/bangladesh-leader-has-left-country-amid-protests-newspaper-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 09:17:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗称希望惩罚以色列但避免全面战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/iran-says-it-aims-to-reestablish-deterrence-against-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗重申希望避免与以色列爆发全面战争，尽管它威胁要对上周哈马斯领导人在伊朗首都遭暗杀事件进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/iran-says-it-aims-to-reestablish-deterrence-against-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 08:02:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
